%md
#### Register a table for the events data

msg.data: Register a table for the events data

paragraphs.text: eventsDF.createOrReplaceTempView("gdeltevents")

//verify data is in the table

spark.sql("SELECT GlobalEventID,SQLDate,Actor1Code, Actor1Name, Actor1CountryCode,Actor1KnownGroupCode,Actor1EthnicCode,Actor1Type1Code from gdeltevents where Actor1CountryCode='GRC'").show(2)

%md
### Analysis

%md
#### Bad events

//checked for total events related to "bad" codes - 13 to 20

spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt FROM gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode IN ('13','14','15','16','17','18','19','20') and Actor1CountryCode is not NULL group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 10").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 13 THREATEN
spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt FROM gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode ='13' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 10").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 14 PROTEST
spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt FROM gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode ='14' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 10").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 15 EXHIBIT FORCE POSTURE

spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt FROM gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode ='15' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 10").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 16 REDUCE RELATIONS

spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt FROM gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode ='16' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 10").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 17 COERCE

spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt FROM gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode ='17' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 10").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 18 ASSAULT

spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt from gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode='18' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 100").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 19 FIGHT
spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt from gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode='19' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC limit 100").show

//checked for any events related to "bad" codes - 20 USE UNCONVENTIONAL MASS VIOLENCE
spark.sql("SELECT Actor1CountryCode, count(EventRootCode) as cnt from gdeltevents WHERE EventRootCode='20' group by Actor1CountryCode order by cnt DESC").show

%md
#### Total Events Using Large Dataset

//count number of events involving Philippines
spark.sql("SELECT COUNT(GlobalEventID) FROM gdeltevents WHERE Actor1CountryCode='PHL'").show

//count number of events involving Mauritius
spark.sql("SELECT COUNT(GlobalEventID) FROM gdeltevents WHERE Actor1CountryCode='MUS'").show

//count number of events involving Senegal
spark.sql("SELECT COUNT(GlobalEventID) FROM gdeltevents WHERE Actor1CountryCode='SEN'").show

//count number of events involving Greece
spark.sql("SELECT COUNT(GlobalEventID) FROM gdeltevents WHERE Actor1CountryCode='GRC'").show

//count number of events involving Chile
spark.sql("SELECT COUNT(GlobalEventID) FROM gdeltevents WHERE Actor1CountryCode='CHL'").show

//count number of events involving Mexico
spark.sql("SELECT COUNT(GlobalEventID) FROM gdeltevents WHERE Actor1CountryCode='MEX'").show

%md
#### Goldstein Scale Using Large Dataset

//goldstein scale in ascending order by actor1countrycode to identify the countries with the lowest scores

spark.sql("select Actor1CountryCode, avg(GoldSteinScale) as ag from gdeltevents group by Actor1CountryCode ORDER BY ag limit 10").show

//in descending order by actor1country code to identify the countires with highest scores

spark.sql("select Actor1CountryCode, avg(GoldSteinScale) as ag from gdeltevents group by Actor1CountryCode ORDER BY ag DESC limit 10").show
